OL,3,CAppeal after boy, 9 and woman
OL,4,Cseriously injured in crash
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fafter a 9-year-old boy and a woman
OL,8,Fwere injured in a car accident in East
OL,9,FMalling, Kent.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called at 1.37
OL,12,Fon Monday 25th May after a blue Audi
OL,13,FA5 and a black Mercedes GLC collided
OL,14,Fin Wateringbury Road, at the junction
OL,15,Fwith Sweets Lane.
OL,17,FThe child was airlifted to a London
OL,18,Fhospital with serious injuries and has
OL,19,Fsince been discharged.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
