OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781524080
OL,3,CAppeal after boy, 9 and woman
OL,4,Cseriously injured in crash
OL,6,FA 39 year old woman was also taken to
OL,7,Fhospital where she remains in a stable
OL,8,Fcondition.
OL,10,FOfficers from the Serious Collision
OL,11,FInvestigation Unit continue their
OL,12,Fenquiries into the circumstances
OL,13,Fsurrounding the incident and urge
OL,14,Fanyone who saw the collision, or who
OL,15,Fmight have seen the vehicles
OL,16,Fbeforehand, to contact police.
OL,18,FMotorists who were in the area are
OL,19,Furged to check for any dashcam
OL,20,Ffootage, which may assist the
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/2
